\sqrt{n}\overline{X}
Y_n=\sqrt{n}*\overline{X}=\sqrt{n}*\sum_{i=1}^{n} Xi/n=\sum_{i=1}^{n} Xi/\sqrt{n}.
M_{Y_n}(t)=E[e^{tY_n}]=E[e^{t*(\sum_{i=1}^{n} Xi/\sqrt{n})}]=E[e^{\frac{t}{\sqrt{n}}X_1}]*E[e^{\frac{t}{\sqrt{n}}X_2}]*...*E[e^{\frac{t}{\sqrt{n}}X_n}]=(E[e^{\frac{t}{\sqrt{n}}X}])^n=(M_X(\frac{t}{\sqrt{n}}))^n
